thread.title: Adam Soar
thread.title_full: Store DJ reviewed by Adam Soar

author: Adam Soar
title: Adam Soar
text:
I've done a lot of business with these guys over the course of about 5 years. I'll always call up to see if they can order something from them, even if it's not listed on their website because I know they'll 100% look after me and do it for the best price I can.
Very professional and polite customer service! Wouldn't even think about shopping somewhere else
